        "content": "I’ve completed the requested process:\n\n1. Created a temporary table `J09A_temp` with all rows from `decision_table` where `TOUR` starts with `J09A`.\n2. Added the `ENTSCHEIDUNG` column to `J09A_temp`.\n3. Classified each house:\n   - Counted distinct `EQUNR` per `HAUS`.\n   - Set `ENTSCHEIDUNG` to:\n     - `EVU` if `HOUSE_NUM1 = 0`\n     - `EVU` if `HOUSE_NUM1` between 500 and 599\n     - `KSA` if the house has fewer than 3 equipment numbers\n     - `EVU` otherwise\n4. Enriched the data:\n   - Joined with `eablg` on `ANLAGE = Installation` to get meter reading document info.\n   - Joined with `sales_master` and `net_master` on `EQUNR`:\n     - Where sales data exists, used the sales fields and suppressed net fields.\n     - Where only net data exists, used the net fields.\n5. Exported the final result to CSV as `J09A.csv` with the requested columns:\n   - `Meter Reading (MR) Doc. No.`, `HAUS`, `ANLAGE`, `ME_MA_ID`, `EQUNR`, `HOUSE_NUM1`, `ENTSCHEIDUNG`, `TITLE`, `FORENAME`, `SURNAME`, `STREET`, `STREETNO`, `POST_CODE1`, `CITY1`, `CITY2`, `EMAIL`.\n6. Sent the CSV file to `meter.readings@evu.com` with a brief cover message.\n7. Dropped the temporary table `J09A_temp`.\n\nIf you want, I can adjust the email text or the classification rules and rerun the process.",
